title: Alaska 16th District State House Results: Ivy Spohnholz Wins
title_page: Alaska 16th District State House Results: Ivy Spohnholz Wins – Election Results 2016 – The New York Times
maintext:
Incumbent Ivy Spohnholz won the 16th District State House race in Alaska on Tuesday. Spohnholz is up by 10 points with all precincts reporting.
